<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[mix all marinade ingredients, until sugar dissolves and add thinly sliced pork. Stand at least 10 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[bring a half filled pot to a boil, add the noodles and bring back to boil. Add 250ml water and bring back to boil, then add 125 ml water and bring back to boil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when noodles are barely tender drain, rinse in hot water and drain]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[chop all garlic, julienne spring onion, separate white and green of cabbage and slice thinly separately]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sieve pork but keep liquid]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[stir fry (hi heat) pork, 40 s, then set aside]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add garlic, spring onion, white part of cabbage, 30 s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[meanwhile put seame oil on medium low fire ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add pork, marinade, green part of cabbage, 20 s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add noodles and cornstarch, 40 s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[fry garlic in sesame oil, 15 s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[serve noodles with sesame oil / garlic mix poured on top]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
